---
title: Learn
layout: main.njk
description: These are all the mini-posts on things I learn as a developer. My aim is to add at least 100 posts to this page. I didn't write 100 yet because most posts I begin writing here get too long and become regular blog posts!
---

<div class="wrapper learn-wrapper">
    <h1 class="title learn-title">Learn</h1>
    <p class="learn-introduction">These are all the mini-posts on things I learn as a developer. There are currently <strong>{{ collections.learn.length }}</strong>. My aim is to add at least 100. I didn't yet because most get too long and become <a href="/blog" class="link-single">regular blog posts</a>!</p>
    <ul class="learn-list">
        {% for p in collections.learn | learnSort %}
            <li>
                <a href="{{ p.url }}">{{ p.data.title }}</a>
                <div class="learn-post-dates">{{ p.data.postdate | readableBlogListDate }}</div>
                <span class="tags learn-post-tags">
                    {% for tag in p.data.tags %}
                        {%- if collections.tagList.indexOf(tag) != -1 -%}
                            {% set tagUrl %}/tags/{{ tag }}/{%endset %}
                            <a href="{{ tagUrl | url }}">{{ tag }}</a>
                        {%- endif -%}
                    {% endfor %}
                </span>
            </li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>
</div>